{
  "stem": "26609.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But later on-- I think I told this story when I went to the-- I was still in my own home, on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I think I said who helped me there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was hidden there many times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that must have been in '42.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because in '42 I was-- I still didn't say about it-- imprisoned in Lackiego.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The Prison was named Lackiego because it was on Lackiego Street, and it was a prison for criminals.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were two prisons in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One was on [INAUDIBLE]-- hard prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now Lackiego, there were political, too-- prisoners-- imprisoned there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I don't want to go back to the story-- maybe it will come later-- about why I was imprisoned.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But after the prison, when I-- and, again, a priest helped me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that's a long story how he helped me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But when I was freed from prison, later on, of course I didn't go back, straight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And my daughter was left with the Polish family-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] small family-- a woman with two children, alone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Very poor, and very awful conditions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I just-- even now, if I think back of it, I don't know how she survived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But when I came back-- not straightaway as I came back, because I was afraid someone was behind me to see where I'm going.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They could find out that I'm not the one that I said in the prison I am.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a night I spent in the city from place to place, in the dark, walking around.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About this I will tell later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's another story.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
